data.text: all of this is from https://t.co/bCbB1ArfE0 , check it out!

REVERSE LUNGE + HIGH KNEE
-holding dumbells at shoulder height, do a lunge
-instead of standing up, lift your other leg all the way up into high knees 
-alternate for 8 reps each side https://t.co/moKaOzvhyX

RENEGADE ROW TO MOUNTAIN CLIMBER
-hold pushup position w/feet hip width apart (A) 
-lift up one dumbbell at a time for 10 reps each side
-switch back to pushup position and raise alternating knees towards your chest for 10 reps each side https://t.co/oH7uu85v5l

OVERHEAD CRUNCH ROTATION 
-hold a medicine ball over your head and do 10 reps of normal crunches holding it (a+b)
-then do 10 more reps each side picking up and rotating to lower the ball outside of your hip (a+c) https://t.co/WaJHeehbUF

BANDED 4X4 WALK
-walk around with a resistance band between your feet
-specifically, shuffle right for 20-30 steps, forward for 20-30 steps, left for 20-30 steps, then backwards like a big square 
-keep tension between your feet the whole time https://t.co/tu4aKJ5ujf

SINGLE DUMBELL CLEAN AND PRESS
-start with weight in between your feet 
-do a squat to pick up the weight (A) 
-pick it up palms in until your shoulder (B)
-flip your palm around and lift it all the way up (C) https://t.co/LPvOfpFAe3
Do this routine 2-3x a week on alternating days. Do 2-5 sets of each exercise with 10-30 second rests in between sets for best results!
